    <p>
        <strong>EditorNeo</strong> is a simple user friendy data editor written in PHP. It consists of a single
        file ready to deploy to the target server. Free for commercial and non-commercial use.
    </p>

    <h2 id="key-features">Key features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Clean modern user interface</li>
        <li>Single database connection</li>
        <li>Data manipulation and searching</li>
        <li>Navigation between related data</li>
        <li>Simplified and localised values formatting</li>
        <li>Extendable by plugins</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 id="supported-databases">Supported databases</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>MySQL, MariaDB, PostgreSQL, MS SQL, SQLite, Oracle</li>
        <li>MongoDB, SimpleDB</li>
